These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different games are played: whist, domino, monopoly, billiard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, april, december, november
1. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in april##2
2. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
4. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person playing monopoly##6
5. the person playing monopoly is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
6. the person playing whist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | billiard  | whist | monopoly | domino  |
| Birthday   | july | december   | november  | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, august, december
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, water-polo, lacrosse, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##8
2. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
3. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who's birthday is in january##2
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday   | august | january          | december | june     |
| Sport    | lacrosse      | weightlifting | biathlon | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, traveling, skydiving, puzzles
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rat, dog, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the goldfish is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
2. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | baking | traveling | skydiving     | puzzles |
| Pet   | rat    | guinea-pig   | goldfish | dog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, september, july
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, poppy, sunflower, orchid
1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
3. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who growssunflower##8
5. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | september   | april         | july   | october    |
| Flower         | poppy | orchid | sunflower | balloon-flower |

