.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, orange, fuchsia, turquise
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, turkish, japanese, british
1. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person who likes red and the person who likes orange##7
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the japanese##5
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes red##7
4. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the british##8
5. the british is somewhere between the person who likes orange and the turkish##7
6. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
7. the turkish is not to the left of the person who likes red##8
8. the turkish is on the left or right of the person who likes turquise##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | orange   | fuchsia | turquise | red    |
| Nationality         | australian | british   | japanese   | turkish |

