.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, engineer, fisherman, police-officer
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, filmmaking, skydiving, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the left of the bartender##5
3. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
5. the bartender is somewhere to the left of the engineer##5
6. the police-officer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
7. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Job          | police-officer | bartender | engineer  | fisherman |
| Hobby   | filmmaking   | puzzles         | skydiving | traveling |

