.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, september, february
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing, camping, reading
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
2. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's hobby is camping##7
3. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
4. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##8
5. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
8. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | august      | september | may | february   |
| Hobby      | puzzles | camping | reading  | rock-climbing |

