.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, bird, goat, hedgehog
4 different games are played: domino, bridge, monopoly, scrabble
1. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
2. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
4. the person playing monopoly is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the owner of the bird##7
5. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person playing bridge and the owner of the goat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Pet     | bird | goat | hedgehog | rat     |
| Game   | domino   | monopoly        | scrabble          | bridge |

