.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, dog, rat
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, zombie, superhero, adventure
1. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the rat and the person watching horror movies##2
2. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the owner of the dog is not the person watching superhero movies##6
7. the owner of the rat is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
8. the person watching horror movies is not to the left of the person watching zombie movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Pet   | rat   | hedgehog | dog | ferret |
| Movie-Genre     | adventure | zombie       | horror  | superhero    |

