.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, ebony, aquamarine, azure
House: wooden, palace, townhouse, craftsman
1. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the craftsman house##8
2. the wooden house is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8
3. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
4. the wooden house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who likes aquamarine is between the craftsman house and the townhouse house##2
6. the person who likes ebony is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color    | ebony        | azure | aquamarine      | red    |
| House   | wooden | townhouse   | palace | craftsman |

