.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, carrot, grapes, lime
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, sunflower, daisy, dahlia
1. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##8
2. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the person eating zucchini##8
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
4. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating lime is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere between the person who growsdaisy and the person eating carrot##7
7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3
8. the person eating lime is on the left or right of the person eating carrot##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | lime | carrot         | grapes    | zucchini       |
| Flower      | sunflower | dahlia | amaryllis | daisy |

