 2. the indian is not to the left of the british##8
 3. the argentine is the cottage house##1
 4. the cottage house is not to the right of the palace house##8
 5. the farmhouse house is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the british##5
 7. the palace house is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the argentine is not to the right of the cottage house##8
 9. the palace house is not to the left of the argentine##8
10. the polish is not to the left of the futuristic house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Nationality          | polish    | british | argentine | indian |
| House   | futuristic | farmhouse  | cottage     | palace    |

