There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, black, ebony, blue
1. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
2. the person who likes black is not to the left of the person eating carrot##8
3. the person who likes ebony is not to the right of the person who likes black##8
4. the person eating tomato is not the person who likes blue##6
5. the person eating nectarine is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
6. the person who likes ivory is on the far right##1
7. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
8. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Food           | tomato | nectarine | carrot | strawberry   |
| Color   | ebony       | blue      | black    | ivory |

