.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, western, fantasy, horror
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, almond-milk, water, coffee
1. the person watching horror movies is not the person drinking water##6
2. the person drinking water is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching horror movies##7
4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
5. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
6. the person drinking juice is not to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##8
7. the person watching western movies is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | adventure  | horror | western  | fantasy  |
| Beverage   | juice | almond-milk   | coffee | water |

