.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, d&b, blues, hip-hop
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, corn, blueberry, papaya
1. the person eating corn is not the fan of salsa##6
2. the person eating blueberry is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is not to the left of the person eating papaya##8
4. the fan of blues is the person eating asparagus##1
5. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the person eating corn and the person eating asparagus##7
6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
7. the person eating blueberry is between the person eating papaya and the fan of blues##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre         | d&b    | hip-hop | salsa | blues |
| Food   | corn | papaya      | blueberry     | asparagus     |

 